Convergent Form, Divergent Voice II — Corpus License

This repository is a research data corpus accompanying the v2 series of
*Convergent Form, Divergent Voice* papers (Tenner & Tenner, 2026). It
contains raw model outputs (data) and the collection / analysis code
(scripts) used to produce them.

