RAW MODEL OUTPUTS

The trace JSON files contain outputs generated by language models from
Anthropic, OpenAI, Google, xAI, DeepSeek, Moonshot AI, MiniMax, Z.ai,
and Alibaba, accessed either directly or via OpenRouter (with explicit
upstream pinning where relevant). Each provider's Terms of Service apply
to the generated content. The release of this data is intended for
research and reproduction purposes; readers who wish to use the content
for other purposes should consult the relevant provider's terms.

The model names, trademarks, and product designations referenced in this
repository (Claude, GPT, Gemini, Grok, DeepSeek, Kimi, MiniMax, GLM,
Qwen) are the property of their respective owners.
